:"2019-08-03T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"全城滅過街老鼠"},{"pid":"4cae69ab46786f994a7d7e02e2484087254d8eca","tid":1402264,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c122e5ee9a0703527e35973b708fc182976a7ff","tid":1402264,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"全城滅過街老鼠"},{"pid":"cca71f3e9e507f3d7c511f25a23ff12de2502d85","tid":1402264,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1443df29b94f485efd89e16635310c52cbcbb952","tid":1402264,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"葵涌，馬鞍山，黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武新戰略應以此方向發展"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"一三五罷買!!<br />\n<br />\n85之後<br />\n<br />\n[參考波蘭成功例子既最佳戰術] 完全剋制政府冷處理 - 罷買 <br />\n一個最有效既長期戰術, 麻煩入去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n1. 週期性罷買係相當可行既一個戰術, 因為更能夠令普通人適應<br />\n2. 罷買影響力可以好大<br />\n3. 政府用冷處理戰術,打算拖至9月,而罷買係開學之後一樣可以實行,可以向社會施加壓力既最好方法<br />\n4. 罷買比遊行, 三罷, 更能夠說服中立派/和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1</a>"}]}